					PC Tune-Ups
				</h1>
				<p class="text-lg text-white/80 sm:text-xl">
					Your neighborhood team for fast, friendly computer and device repair
					in the Greater New Orleans area—with 10+ years of hands-on experience.
				</p>
				<ul class="grid gap-3 text-sm text-white/80 sm:grid-cols-2">
					<li>
						<strong>Address:</strong> 5416 Veterans Blvd, Metairie, LA 70003
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Phone:</strong>
						<a class="underline hover:text-emerald-200" href="tel:15048851635"
							>1-504-885-1635</a>
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Email:</strong>
						<a
							class="underline hover:text-emerald-200"
							href="mailto:info@afcom-inc.com">info@afcom-inc.com</a
						>
						·
						<a
							class="underline hover:text-emerald-200"
							href="mailto:sales@afcom-inc.com">sales@afcom-inc.com</a
						>
					</li>
