							day."
						</p>
						<p class="mt-4 text-sm text-white/60">
							— <strong>Mike</strong>, Kenner
						</p>
					</blockquote>
					<blockquote class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
						<p class="text-lg text-white">
