						</p>
						<p class="mt-4 text-sm text-white/60">
							— <strong>Damian</strong>, Metairie
						</p>
					</blockquote>
				</div>
			</section>

			<hr class="border-white/10" />

			<section class="space-y-4" id="contact">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
					Service Area &amp; Next Steps
				</h2>
				<p class="text-white/80">
					We proudly serve Metairie, Kenner, New Orleans, and surrounding
					communities.
				</p>
				<p class="text-white/80">
					Stop by our shop, call 1-504-885-1635, or email <a
						class="underline hover:text-emerald-200"
						href="mailto:info@afcom-inc.com">info@afcom-inc.com</a
					> for a free estimate—let's get your tech tuned up today.
				</p>
			</section>
		</main>

